@{b}Radder v1.0@{ub}

Radder v1.0

Radder is a tool which allows you to keep the contents of your RAD disk
intact even after you turn off your Amiga at the power for the night.
All you have to do is choose Shut Down from your tools menu when Radder
is running and then you will be able to shut down your computer and
use your RAD disk with all the info intact the next time you start up.


@endnode
